params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard shows Alert overview related to the Prisma Cloud Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the detection of the ingested alerts from Prisma Cloud.

It displays total count of alerts. Also shows the distribution of alerts by cloud providers, status, cloud service name, resource type, policy severity and time. Details regarding alert resource and alert policy are also shown.
It fetches new updates every 1 minute by default.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/prisma_cloud/overview)**
